Duration: 1 turn

Weight: 1~

@900000022 = ~Vitriolic Ooze~
@900000023 = ~This potion smells and tastes awful.  Anybody that drinks it finds that any ability or spell they cast that deals acid damage deals an additional 50% damage for 1 turn.

STATISTICS:

Special: +50% acid damage
Duration: 1 turn

Weight: 1~

@900000024 = ~Storm Brew~
@900000025 = ~A small flash of lightning seems to dance in the middle of this potion.  Anybody that drinks it finds that any ability or spell they cast that deals electrical damage deals an additional 50% damage for 1 turn.

STATISTICS:

Special: +50% electrical damage
Duration: 1 turn

Weight: 1~

