Charge abilities:
- Force
  Range: 60-ft.
  Damage: 2d6 magic damage (save for 1/2)
  Special: Knocks non-huge creature back 10' if no save vs. wands is made.
  Area of Effect: 1 creature

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~
